description:
SubscriberGroupProfile: Configuration parameters for subscriber groups in a 5G/NR network.

dateTime: Timestamp of the record.
Area_Name: Geographic area of the cell.
CellId: Unique identifier of the cell site.
Id2: Duplicate of CellId.
Id3: QoS class identifier (QCI) or ENDC indication.
vsDataType: Data type identifier.
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format.
SubscriberGroupProfile.userLabel: User-defined label for the profile.
SubscriberGroupProfile.bearerTriggerList: List of bearer triggers for the profile.
SubscriberGroupProfile.sCellScheduleSinrThresOffset: SINR threshold offset for secondary cells.
SubscriberGroupProfile.subGroupConfiguration2: Configuration parameter for subgroup 2.
SubscriberGroupProfile.ulPlThresToRegion: Uplink power limit threshold.
SubscriberGroupProfile.subGroupConfiguration1: Configuration parameter for subgroup 1.
SubscriberGroupProfile.subGroupConfiguration4: Configuration parameter for subgroup 4.
SubscriberGroupProfile.subGroupConfiguration3: Configuration parameter for subgroup 3.
SubscriberGroupProfile.subscriberGroupProfileId: Unique identifier of the subscriber group profile.
SubscriberGroupProfile.dlHarqBlerTarget: Target downlink HARQ Block Error Rate.
SubscriberGroupProfile.subGroupConfiguration6: Configuration parameter for subgroup 6.
SubscriberGroupProfile.subGroupConfiguration5: Configuration parameter for subgroup 5.
SubscriberGroupProfile.preschedulingMode: Prescheduling mode configuration.
SubscriberGroupProfile.groupExtendInactAfterVolteRel: Group extension inactivity after VoLTE release.
SubscriberGroupProfile.featuresToDisableMeas: Features to disable for measurements.
SubscriberGroupProfile.customTriggerType: Type of custom trigger.
SubscriberGroupProfile.iuaProfileRef: Reference to the Inter-cell User Association profile.
SubscriberGroupProfile.profileIndex: Index of the profile.
SubscriberGroupProfile.spidTriggerList: List of SPID triggers.
SubscriberGroupProfile.cellTriggerList: List of cell triggers.
SubscriberGroupProfile.ulCandidateToRegion: Flag indicating if uplink candidate is used for region selection.
SubscriberGroupProfile.ulMcsUpperLimit: Upper limit for uplink MCS.
SubscriberGroupProfile.pZeroNominalPuschOffset: Nominal PUSCH offset for P0.
SubscriberGroupProfile.qciOffsetForQCI9: QCI offset for QCI 9.
SubscriberGroupProfile.drxMode: Discontinuous reception (DRX) mode.
SubscriberGroupProfile.qciOffsetForQCI8: QCI offset for QCI 8.
SubscriberGroupProfile.dlDynBlerTargetMin: Minimum downlink dynamic BLER target.
SubscriberGroupProfile.selectionProbability: Probability of selecting the profile.
SubscriberGroupProfile.pZeroNominalPucchOffset: Nominal PUCCH offset for P0.
SubscriberGroupProfile.qciOffsetForQCI7: QCI offset for QCI 7.
SubscriberGroupProfile.qciOffsetForQCI6: QCI offset for QCI 6.
SubscriberGroupProfile.lastSchedLinkAdaptMode: Last scheduled link adaptation mode.
SubscriberGroupProfile.preschedProfileRef: Reference to the prescheduling profile.
SubscriberGroupProfile.dlDynBlerTargetAlg: Algorithm for dynamic downlink BLER target.
SubscriberGroupProfile.iuaMode: Inter-cell user association mode.
SubscriberGroupProfile.profilePriority: Priority of the profile.
SubscriberGroupProfile.ulHarqBlerTarget: Target uplink HARQ Block Error Rate.
SubscriberGroupProfile.customTriggerList: List of custom triggers.
SubscriberGroupProfile.caRateAdjustCoeff: CA rate adjustment coefficient.
SubscriberGroupProfile.dlAiLaDeltaSinrMax: Maximum delta SINR for downlink AI-LA.
SubscriberGroupProfile.dlDynBlerTargetMax: Maximum downlink dynamic BLER target.
SubscriberGroupProfile.fastACqiReportEnabled: Flag indicating if fast A-CQI reporting is enabled.
SubscriberGroupProfile.ulSinrThresToRegion: Uplink SINR threshold.
SubscriberGroupProfile.pdcchFlexibleBlerMode: PDCCH flexible BLER mode.
SubscriberGroupProfile.ulMcsLowerLimit: Lower limit for uplink MCS.
SubscriberGroupProfile.subGroupConfiguration7: Configuration parameter for subgroup 7.
SubscriberGroupProfile.endcUserProfileRef: Reference to the ENDC user profile.
